'''間皮細胞'''(Mesothelium)是指構成間皮的[[細胞|細胞]]，間皮由一層細胞組成，位在[[胸膜|胸膜]]或[[腹膜|腹膜]]，心包腔内和[[器官|器官]]相接之面上。間皮的功用是提供[[潤滑|潤滑]]，使器官與器官、器官與胸膜與腹膜間都能得到良好的保護，不會互相磨損受傷。而間皮所提供的潤滑和保護作用就是靠間皮細胞所分泌的物質來達成。多半為[[細胞外基質|細胞外基質]]、[[玻尿酸|玻尿酸]]類物質。<ref name="pmid14592528">{{cite journal |author=Mutsaers SE |title=The mesothelial cell |journal=Int. J. Biochem. Cell Biol. |volume=36 |issue=1 |pages=9–16, 2004PMID 14592528 |doi= |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1357272503002425 |access-date=2008-06-18 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713001344/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1357272503002425 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="pmid12153683">{{cite journal |author=Mutsaers SE |title=Mesothelial cells: their structure, function and role in serosal repair |journal=Respirology |volume=7 |issue=3 |pages=171–91, 2002 PMID 12153683 |doi= |url=http://www.blackwell-synergy.com/openurl?genre=article&sid=nlm:pubmed&issn=1323-7799&date=2002&volume=7&issue=3&spage=171 }}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name="pmid15362999">{{cite journal |author=Leard LE, Broaddus VC |title=Mesothelial cell proliferation and apoptosis |journal=Respirology |volume=9 |issue=3 |pages=292–9, 2004 PMID 15362999 |doi=10.1111/j.1440-1843.2004.00602.x |url=}}</ref>

